<Layout title="About Us">
  <section class="bg-white text-orange-900 px-6 py-12 md:px-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-6">About Us</h1>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        At <strong class="text-orange-700">Proprio+</strong>, we believe property management should be simple, transparent, and worry-free. Born out of a passion for real estate and a commitment to excellence, our company was founded by experienced professionals who saw an opportunity to do things better—for property owners, tenants, and communities alike.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        After years of working within the industry, we realized that many property owners were looking for more than just maintenance and rent collection—they wanted a team they could trust. That's why we started Proprio+: to offer reliable, personal, and results-driven property management services that give our clients peace of mind.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-500 mt-10 mb-4">What We Do</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We specialize in full-service property management, handling everything from tenant placement and rent collection to maintenance, inspections, and 24/7 support. Whether you own a single unit or a growing portfolio, we tailor our services to fit your needs and ensure your property is well-managed, profitable, and cared for.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-500 mt-10 mb-4">More Than Just Management</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        One of the things that sets <strong class="text-orange-700">Proprio+</strong> apart is our in-house <strong>licensed real estate agent</strong>, which allows us to offer a complete and seamless experience. Thanks to this added expertise, we’re able to provide:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-orange-900">
        <li>Access to <strong>exclusive listings</strong> on premium platforms like <strong>Centris</strong></li>
        <li>Professional <strong>property marketing</strong> for rentals or sales</li>
        <li>Expert <strong>guidance on buying, selling, or optimizing</strong> your investments</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Whether you're looking to fill a vacancy, grow your portfolio, or sell a property, you’ll benefit from an integrated, one-stop solution—no need to juggle multiple service providers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-500 mt-10 mb-4">Why Choose Us?</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-orange-900">
        <li><strong>Experienced & Professional:</strong> Practical knowledge and a proactive approach.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparent & Honest:</strong> Open communication and no surprises.</li>
        <li><strong>Fully Featured Service:</strong> From maintenance to marketing to sales.</li>
        <li><strong>Local & Responsive:</strong> Proudly serving our community with quick response times.</li>
        <li><strong>Personalized Support:</strong> We treat every property like our own.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        At <strong class="text-orange-700">Proprio+</strong>, we’re more than just property managers—we’re your dedicated real estate partners.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-orange-100 p-6 rounded-xl mt-10 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-700 mb-2">Let’s Work Together</h3>
        <p class="mb-4 text-orange-900">Ready to take the stress out of managing your property?</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Contact Us Today
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
